A good war movie; it sets you in the mood of the Vietnam war; he is very violent and bloody;

in the course of the film i am inspired by the game metal gear solid, where a hero needs to kill the villain who rebelled against his country but in fact there is something more complex involved about this villain;

This film could be seen without knowing how it was produced because it may disappoint some because of the problems that happened.

Mandatory war film and for cinema lovers!
